data.value: How to use this application: Browse: select file Shot Detection: Different algorithms for shot detection Press on load in the Shot Detection window load the shots of the last algorithm in the main form. You're then able to play shots and add tags to the shots by selecting the shot. Retrieve Shots: type in a keyword in the textbox above, and the application will show every shot with that tag. By pressing retrieve shot without any character in the textbox you can go back to all the shots. Export Frame: exports the current frame that is playing Export as XML: export all the shots of a video in an XML-file
